  "_comment_national": "National teams (World Cup / EUROs / friendlies). Providers name dedicated per-game channels with broadcast forms the canonical Football-Data name lacks: 'USA' for United States, and Spanish exonyms on '- En Espanol' feeds (Estados Unidos, Alemania, Brasil). Values are matched as case-insensitive SUBSTRINGS and the channel-name match requires BOTH teams, so full-word Spanish exonyms are safe; bare 2-3 letter FIFA codes are deliberately omitted (too substring-collision-prone, e.g. 'POR' in 'sport'). Accented and unaccented Spanish forms are both listed since provider EPGs are inconsistent. See #123.",

